WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.350
Hey, good morning, family. Thank you for

00:00:02.360 --> 00:00:05.590
joining us today. Well, it's Diana and I

00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:07.230
again, and I'm excited she's with

00:00:07.240 --> 00:00:11.509
me today. My best friend is with me—my hottie.

00:00:11.519 --> 00:00:15.910
After all these years,

00:00:15.920 --> 00:00:18.310
I'm still smitten over this girl.

00:00:18.320 --> 00:00:20.950
She is my best friend, and I'm so

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:23.109
thankful that she's with me. Best friend,

00:00:23.119 --> 00:00:27.029
too. We're here at our spot. I come here

00:00:27.039 --> 00:00:30.990
because it inspires me.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:32.990
I know I've said this before, folks, but

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:37.830
I love the ORU campus. Make no little plans

00:00:37.840 --> 00:00:42.350
here. God is about to show up and show

00:00:42.360 --> 00:00:45.670
off at this campus. There was a lady that

00:00:45.680 --> 00:00:49.029
sent us a flyer in the mail about all

00:00:49.039 --> 00:00:51.510
the revivals that are taking place

00:00:51.520 --> 00:00:54.549
across the nation on college campuses.

00:00:54.559 --> 00:00:56.910
Whenever she sent that to me, I guess

00:00:56.920 --> 00:00:58.830
she was saying, 'Hey, look, it's

00:00:58.840 --> 00:01:00.549
happening other

00:01:00.549 --> 00:01:00.559
places.'But

00:01:00.559 --> 00:01:02.750
I'm telling you, this will be the

00:01:02.750 --> 00:01:02.760
mega-revival

00:01:02.760 --> 00:01:06.630
at this school with

00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:10.109
Victory across the street

00:01:10.109 --> 00:01:10.119
there—big

00:01:10.119 --> 00:01:13.749
victory with Paul Daugherty. I believe

00:01:13.759 --> 00:01:16.550
we're about to see one of the greatest

00:01:16.560 --> 00:01:19.670
revivals this world has ever seen.

00:01:19.680 --> 00:01:21.429
People say, 'Hey, Brandon, what

00:01:21.439 --> 00:01:23.630
do you do for a living?'and everything,

00:01:23.640 --> 00:01:25.469
and want to know what Diana and I do.

00:01:25.479 --> 00:01:28.230
Do you all work? Yes, we do eBay and

00:01:28.240 --> 00:01:30.990
Poshmark, and we continue to do that.

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:33.030
It's made a good living for us, and

00:01:33.040 --> 00:01:35.230
we're thankful for it. We find

00:01:35.240 --> 00:01:37.270
stuff at thrift stores and we go into

00:01:37.280 --> 00:01:38.990
these thrift stores and we buy used

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:40.870
stuff, and we turn it around for a

00:01:40.880 --> 00:01:43.429
profit. We'll continue to do that. We

00:01:43.439 --> 00:01:45.630
enjoy doing it. We like working

00:01:45.640 --> 00:01:47.590
together and we'll continue to work

00:01:47.600 --> 00:01:49.709
there. Who wants to work for the world if

00:01:49.719 --> 00:01:51.109
you can work for yourself and make

00:01:51.119 --> 00:01:52.709
better money than

00:01:52.719 --> 00:01:54.630
you do for the world? I think it's

00:01:54.640 --> 00:01:56.630
pretty smart on our

00:01:56.640 --> 00:02:00.429
part. God led

00:02:00.429 --> 00:02:00.439
us.

00:02:00.439 --> 00:02:03.870
Diana is the one that came

00:02:03.880 --> 00:02:06.389
up with the idea through the Holy Spirit,

00:02:06.399 --> 00:02:09.229
and the Lord shows me where to go and

00:02:09.239 --> 00:02:11.510
Diana goes in and gets it. That's the

00:02:11.520 --> 00:02:13.309
way we've done it, and that's how I've

00:02:13.319 --> 00:02:16.509
practiced His presence: listening to Him

00:02:16.519 --> 00:02:19.430
for ideas of how to get wealth. I don't

00:02:19.440 --> 00:02:22.830
just sit there and wait idly by saying,

00:02:22.840 --> 00:02:25.710
'God, where's my blessing?'I go out and

00:02:25.720 --> 00:02:28.670
take the land, and we take it

00:02:28.680 --> 00:02:30.630
by force, don't we, babe? We're not

00:02:30.640 --> 00:02:33.150
going to sit back and

00:02:33.160 --> 00:02:36.589
just wait for a mailbox miracle.

00:02:36.599 --> 00:02:39.070
Lottery

00:02:39.070 --> 00:02:39.080
mentality—now

00:02:39.080 --> 00:02:40.949
if the Lord wants to bring it that way,

00:02:40.959 --> 00:02:43.030
fine. Like I've told her, we

00:02:43.040 --> 00:02:45.110
believe in being debt-free and living

00:02:45.120 --> 00:02:47.550
that way. If God doesn't provide it, we

00:02:47.560 --> 00:02:49.830
don't have it. We believe that God is the

00:02:49.840 --> 00:02:52.910
one that abundantly supplies every need

00:02:52.920 --> 00:02:55.270
we have, and that's the way we've

00:02:55.280 --> 00:02:59.910
lived our life.

00:02:59.920 --> 00:03:01.910
We go and find stuff and we can flip

00:03:01.920 --> 00:03:04.149
it on Craigslist

00:03:04.149 --> 00:03:04.159
or

00:03:04.159 --> 00:03:06.470
Facebook Marketplace. There

00:03:06.470 --> 00:03:06.480
are

00:03:06.480 --> 00:03:10.190
creative ideas to do things.

00:03:10.200 --> 00:03:13.190
When we come to ORU and we sit out here,

00:03:13.190 --> 00:03:13.200
it's

00:03:13.200 --> 00:03:14.910
because we know what's coming. What

00:03:14.920 --> 00:03:17.589
the Lord has told us—we know that

00:03:17.599 --> 00:03:20.430
building is going to be filled to

00:03:20.440 --> 00:03:23.550
capacity, the Mabee Center over there.

00:03:23.560 --> 00:03:24.869
Is that what it's called? Yeah, the

00:03:24.869 --> 00:03:24.879
Mabee

00:03:24.879 --> 00:03:28.149
Center. Yes, we believe that

00:03:28.159 --> 00:03:30.390
building is going to be filled to

00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:32.990
capacity with the fire. The

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:35.470
Holy Ghost fire is going to be over that

00:03:35.480 --> 00:03:38.190
building. Now you say, 'Brandon, you

00:03:38.200 --> 00:03:40.630
spoke so poorly about Florida and

00:03:40.640 --> 00:03:43.830
about these other

00:03:43.830 --> 00:03:43.840
areas.'Folks,

00:03:43.840 --> 00:03:46.710
I'm just being real with you.

00:03:46.720 --> 00:03:48.990
I don't mean to be offensive to

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:51.509
anybody and where you live, but I'm just

00:03:51.519 --> 00:03:53.830
real. I tell you what I feel when I go

00:03:53.840 --> 00:03:57.309
into your area. Now, can you change it? Was

00:03:57.319 --> 00:03:59.149
I saying, 'Oh, we got to run from the

00:03:59.159 --> 00:04:01.030
demonic, you got to leave

00:04:01.030 --> 00:04:01.040
Miami?'No.

00:04:01.040 --> 00:04:03.910
God did not station

00:04:03.920 --> 00:04:07.069
me there, and He will equip who He's

00:04:07.079 --> 00:04:10.309
called there to deal with what's there.

00:04:10.319 --> 00:04:11.869
I believe you if you say, 'Well, I

00:04:11.879 --> 00:04:13.030
don't feel it because I'm

00:04:13.030 --> 00:04:13.040
here.'Well,

00:04:13.040 --> 00:04:14.910
God's called you to be there, but He

00:04:14.920 --> 00:04:17.390
didn't call me to be there. So He didn't

00:04:17.400 --> 00:04:19.229
tell me to go in. It's like going into

00:04:19.239 --> 00:04:21.789
somebody's backyard. Me as a prophetic

00:04:21.799 --> 00:04:23.030
voice saying, 'I'm going to go into your

00:04:23.040 --> 00:04:24.909
backyard and take authority over what's

00:04:24.919 --> 00:04:26.710
going on'—He didn't give

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:28.909
me authority there to do that. He didn't

00:04:28.919 --> 00:04:30.430
assign me there.

00:04:30.440 --> 00:04:32.590
I was there on vacation with my

00:04:32.600 --> 00:04:34.590
family to go to Billy Burke and to

00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:38.430
listen to him because I

00:04:38.440 --> 00:04:41.310
want impartation. I'm wanting to learn

00:04:41.320 --> 00:04:43.469
how to flow in the healing anointing

00:04:43.479 --> 00:04:45.790
because,

00:04:45.790 --> 00:04:45.800
as

00:04:45.800 --> 00:04:47.270
I told Diana,

00:04:47.280 --> 00:04:48.990
there's not a lot of

00:04:49.000 --> 00:04:52.310
elders in the church that take the time

00:04:52.320 --> 00:04:55.790
to impart into the younger generation, so

00:04:55.800 --> 00:04:57.950
you have to learn it by trial and

00:04:57.960 --> 00:05:00.390
error. A lot of what we've learned is

00:05:00.400 --> 00:05:02.510
through trial and error. There

00:05:02.510 --> 00:05:02.520
are

00:05:02.520 --> 00:05:04.150
times, like I've told you all

00:05:04.160 --> 00:05:06.629
with Megan, whenever I had that

00:05:06.639 --> 00:05:09.310
visitation from the Lord,

00:05:09.320 --> 00:05:10.950
He took me

00:05:10.960 --> 00:05:13.189
back in the past. I was

00:05:13.199 --> 00:05:14.590
complaining about the shots and the

00:05:14.600 --> 00:05:16.310
things that I had done through the flu

00:05:16.320 --> 00:05:19.309
vaccination, and three weeks later Megan

00:05:19.319 --> 00:05:22.189
was not able to talk.

00:05:22.199 --> 00:05:24.230
I

00:05:24.240 --> 00:05:25.629
remember I was telling the

00:05:25.629 --> 00:05:25.639
Lord—He

00:05:25.639 --> 00:05:27.469
could hear my heart—I said, 'Man, if I

00:05:27.479 --> 00:05:29.830
could just go back to the past and

00:05:29.840 --> 00:05:32.950
change the decisions I've made. If I

00:05:32.960 --> 00:05:35.990
could just have a moment to tell my

00:05:36.000 --> 00:05:38.550
younger self, "Don't get the flu shot,

00:05:38.560 --> 00:05:41.270
don't do these things for

00:05:41.270 --> 00:05:41.280
Megan."'Because

00:05:41.280 --> 00:05:42.350
I didn't know she was going to have

00:05:42.350 --> 00:05:42.360
an

00:05:42.360 --> 00:05:45.150
allergic reaction to it. I didn't know

00:05:45.160 --> 00:05:47.710
all that stuff. But I thought in my mind

00:05:47.720 --> 00:05:49.870
all the time, and when the Lord woke me

00:05:49.880 --> 00:05:51.590
up and He took me out of my body,

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:54.230
He took me back

00:05:54.240 --> 00:05:58.309
to my past. He showed me the power of a

00:05:58.319 --> 00:06:01.950
decision. But He also showed

00:06:01.960 --> 00:06:05.430
me how that decision

00:06:05.440 --> 00:06:06.830
changed

00:06:06.840 --> 00:06:10.670
me for the

00:06:10.680 --> 00:06:13.230
better. Then He told me,

00:06:13.240 --> 00:06:16.110
'You're not big enough,

00:06:16.120 --> 00:06:19.589
Brandon, with your past decisions to mess

00:06:19.599 --> 00:06:22.230
up you and Diana's

00:06:22.230 --> 00:06:22.240
life.'He

00:06:22.240 --> 00:06:25.990
said, 'The steps of the righteous

00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:29.150
are ordered by the Lord, and what the

00:06:29.160 --> 00:06:31.749
devil meant for

00:06:31.759 --> 00:06:35.029
bad, I will turn around for good in your

00:06:35.039 --> 00:06:38.390
favor. I did not cause this with your

00:06:38.400 --> 00:06:41.629
daughter, Brandon. The devil comes to kill,

00:06:41.639 --> 00:06:44.189
steal, and destroy, but I'm going to turn

00:06:44.199 --> 00:06:47.550
it around for good for you.'All the

00:06:47.560 --> 00:06:50.670
pressure, all the stuff that you've

00:06:50.670 --> 00:06:50.680
gone

00:06:50.680 --> 00:06:52.390
through in the past

00:06:52.400 --> 00:06:54.629
will shape you into what you need

00:06:54.639 --> 00:06:57.550
to be for the future if you do not adopt

00:06:57.550 --> 00:06:57.560
a

00:06:57.560 --> 00:07:00.390
victim mentality.

00:07:00.400 --> 00:07:03.070
Do not allow your circumstances from

00:07:03.080 --> 00:07:06.029
your past to dictate your

00:07:06.039 --> 00:07:10.110
future. I will not allow the circumstance

00:07:10.120 --> 00:07:13.589
of what I have been through to dictate

00:07:13.599 --> 00:07:14.749
my

00:07:14.759 --> 00:07:17.550
tomorrow. I'm not going to be a victim;

00:07:17.560 --> 00:07:20.070
I'm a victor. We've said that over

00:07:20.080 --> 00:07:22.110
and over and over again.

00:07:29.919 --> 00:07:32.430
Whenever I

00:07:32.440 --> 00:07:35.309
saw the power of a choice and a

00:07:35.319 --> 00:07:38.830
decision displayed in front of my

00:07:38.840 --> 00:07:40.749
face—how

00:07:40.759 --> 00:07:44.270
the pressure of raising a child with

00:07:44.280 --> 00:07:48.070
special needs and autism has changed me

00:07:48.070 --> 00:07:48.080
and

00:07:48.080 --> 00:07:51.430
changed Diana for the better—I

00:07:51.430 --> 00:07:51.440
realized

00:07:51.440 --> 00:07:53.510
God's on your

00:07:53.520 --> 00:07:56.510
side.

00:07:56.520 --> 00:07:59.629
Whatever you

00:07:59.639 --> 00:08:02.710
have been through, always stay on God's

00:08:02.720 --> 00:08:04.149
side. Even if you don't understand why

00:08:04.159 --> 00:08:05.909
you're going through

00:08:05.919 --> 00:08:09.510
it, always stay on God's side. My favorite

00:08:09.520 --> 00:08:11.710
saying is, 'God is a good God and the

00:08:11.720 --> 00:08:13.749
devil is a bad devil.'Oral

00:08:13.749 --> 00:08:13.759
Roberts—just

00:08:13.759 --> 00:08:15.990
like what we're here at his

00:08:15.990 --> 00:08:16.000
university—it's

00:08:16.000 --> 00:08:18.270
such a beautiful

00:08:18.280 --> 00:08:21.749
university where, you know, 'Make no

00:08:21.759 --> 00:08:24.550
little plans in life, believing God for

00:08:24.550 --> 00:08:24.560
big.'I'm

00:08:24.560 --> 00:08:25.869
going to tell you, a lot of

00:08:25.879 --> 00:08:27.309
people get mad. They say, 'Well, you got a

00:08:27.319 --> 00:08:31.469
nice car.'Of course I believe God for big!

00:08:31.479 --> 00:08:33.870
You

00:08:33.880 --> 00:08:35.230
believe God for favor. We have favor at

00:08:35.240 --> 00:08:37.190
the dealership; we have favor

00:08:37.200 --> 00:08:39.990
wherever you go. You

00:08:39.990 --> 00:08:40.000
sow

00:08:40.000 --> 00:08:42.350
a seed for it.

00:08:42.360 --> 00:08:44.350
We keep selling on eBay

00:08:44.360 --> 00:08:46.710
and we grow our business. I'm never going

00:08:46.720 --> 00:08:49.030
to embrace poverty, folks. So if you don't

00:08:49.040 --> 00:08:50.630
want to see me get blessed, don't watch

00:08:50.640 --> 00:08:52.070
this channel, because this is just the

00:08:52.080 --> 00:08:55.350
beginning. I believe it's time for

00:08:55.360 --> 00:08:57.110
exceedingly, abundantly above all that

00:08:57.120 --> 00:09:00.670
you dare ask or think. I believe that the

00:09:00.680 --> 00:09:02.430
things that the Lord has spoken to me

00:09:02.440 --> 00:09:04.870
prophetically when I pray and intercede

00:09:04.880 --> 00:09:07.670
about the end-time wealth

00:09:07.670 --> 00:09:07.680
transfer—it's

00:09:07.680 --> 00:09:09.350
not for me to just stay where we were

00:09:09.360 --> 00:09:11.829
with eBay and

00:09:11.839 --> 00:09:13.790
Poshmark, and my wife sitting

00:09:13.800 --> 00:09:15.269
there typing all night and

00:09:15.279 --> 00:09:17.310
looking for things in

00:09:17.320 --> 00:09:18.870
the thrift stores. I'm not going to do

00:09:18.880 --> 00:09:21.949
that forever. Right now we do it, but

00:09:21.959 --> 00:09:25.150
there will be an expiration date to that.

00:09:27.640 --> 00:09:29.710
The Lord's

00:09:29.720 --> 00:09:32.350
already told us there'll be a day when

00:09:32.360 --> 00:09:34.750
this stops, but right now it's what He

00:09:34.760 --> 00:09:36.630
wants us to do, and we're thankful for it.

00:09:38.160 --> 00:09:41.910
Wherever God stations you,

00:09:41.920 --> 00:09:44.949
whatever God puts you to do, always do it

00:09:44.959 --> 00:09:46.470
with a joyful attitude and a good

00:09:46.480 --> 00:09:49.470
heart. Don't complain your way through it,

00:09:49.480 --> 00:09:51.430
because the more you complain, even in

00:09:51.440 --> 00:09:53.030
your heart, you'll

00:09:53.040 --> 00:09:55.790
stay there until you get your heart

00:09:55.800 --> 00:09:58.389
right. I've learned if you want promotion

00:09:58.399 --> 00:10:00.630
from the Lord,

00:10:02.560 --> 00:10:05.910
you've got to be

00:10:05.920 --> 00:10:07.509
faithful with the little and God will make

00:10:07.519 --> 00:10:11.230
you ruler over much. Say, 'God, no matter

00:10:11.240 --> 00:10:13.790
where I'm at, no matter what I'm

00:10:13.790 --> 00:10:13.800
doing—cleaning

00:10:13.800 --> 00:10:16.509
toilets or

00:10:16.519 --> 00:10:19.069
cleaning stains out of a

00:10:19.079 --> 00:10:21.230
garment that I found at a thrift

00:10:21.230 --> 00:10:21.240
store—I'm

00:10:21.240 --> 00:10:23.030
thankful.'I

00:10:23.040 --> 00:10:25.269
remember

00:10:25.279 --> 00:10:26.910
before when I was living on food

00:10:26.920 --> 00:10:29.310
stamps, and I'm thankful, Father, for this

00:10:29.320 --> 00:10:31.630
garment. Yeah, it's a Burberry or

00:10:31.640 --> 00:10:34.069
whatever I found today that has a

00:10:34.079 --> 00:10:36.470
coffee stain on it, but Lord, give me an

00:10:36.480 --> 00:10:39.710
anointing to get that coffee stain out.

00:10:39.720 --> 00:10:42.949
Give me an anointing to get that

00:10:42.959 --> 00:10:46.190
ketchup stain out. He has taught me

00:10:46.200 --> 00:10:48.990
how to do things, and

00:10:49.000 --> 00:10:51.430
we've learned how to get stains out. It's

00:10:51.440 --> 00:10:53.949
pretty cool. But it's

00:10:53.959 --> 00:10:56.030
hearing His voice. You say, 'Well, I

00:10:56.040 --> 00:10:58.230
don't hear the voice of the Lord.'I don't

00:10:58.240 --> 00:11:02.150
believe you. The Bible says

00:11:02.160 --> 00:11:04.230
we will

00:11:04.240 --> 00:11:05.990
hear the Good Shepherd's voice, and a

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:08.949
stranger's voice we will not

00:11:08.959 --> 00:11:11.550
follow. I believe the Bible more than I

00:11:11.560 --> 00:11:13.110
believe you. You know why you don't hear

00:11:13.120 --> 00:11:14.269
Him? Because you have too much of

00:11:14.279 --> 00:11:16.990
yourself in the way. If you say you don't

00:11:17.000 --> 00:11:18.110
hear the voice of the Lord, it's because

00:11:18.110 --> 00:11:18.120
you've

00:11:18.120 --> 00:11:21.230
got too much self. Every believer

00:11:21.240 --> 00:11:23.269
has the opportunity to hear the voice of

00:11:23.279 --> 00:11:25.590
the Lord. A child can hear the voice of

00:11:25.600 --> 00:11:28.829
the Lord.

00:11:30.519 --> 00:11:35.310
Die to self daily and listen to

00:11:35.320 --> 00:11:37.509
Him. Be filled with and controlled by the

00:11:37.509 --> 00:11:37.519
Spirit.

00:11:37.519 --> 00:11:39.310
There's no shortcuts, is there, babe? We

00:11:39.320 --> 00:11:41.110
were talking to somebody the other day

00:11:41.120 --> 00:11:43.870
and Diana said, 'Brandon,

00:11:43.880 --> 00:11:46.230
they didn't hear anything you said.'She said

00:11:51.399 --> 00:11:53.710
they

00:11:53.720 --> 00:11:56.150
wanted an easy way; they wanted a shortcut. There's no

00:11:56.160 --> 00:11:58.870
shortcuts. You can

00:11:58.880 --> 00:12:02.550
discern whether

00:12:02.560 --> 00:12:04.629
they're receiving or not.

00:12:04.639 --> 00:12:06.350
Within 15 minutes, the Lord always shows

00:12:06.360 --> 00:12:08.710
me

00:12:08.720 --> 00:12:11.150
if they're receiving

00:12:11.160 --> 00:12:13.230
or if they're not.

00:12:13.240 --> 00:12:16.030
Either you catch it or you

00:12:16.040 --> 00:12:18.189
don't, but there's no

00:12:18.199 --> 00:12:21.550
shortcuts. There's only hard work, and

00:12:21.560 --> 00:12:24.790
anything worth doing is worth doing

00:12:31.279 --> 00:12:32.269
well.

00:12:35.399 --> 00:12:37.949
This is the

00:12:37.959 --> 00:12:39.550
only body that you're ever going to have.

00:12:39.560 --> 00:12:41.269
People want six-packs, but they don't want

00:12:41.279 --> 00:12:43.870
to go to the gym. I'm speaking of me.

00:12:43.870 --> 00:12:43.880
I'd

00:12:43.880 --> 00:12:45.750
love to look like Arnold

00:12:45.760 --> 00:12:47.069
Schwarzenegger, but it takes a lot of

00:12:47.079 --> 00:12:49.189
work to look like him. It takes

00:12:49.199 --> 00:12:51.470
work

00:12:53.639 --> 00:12:56.509
to eat right and exercise.

00:12:58.199 --> 00:13:00.550
Everybody has the same

00:13:00.560 --> 00:13:04.430
ability, the same 24 hours, the same seven days a

00:13:04.440 --> 00:13:07.870
week. You can be a spiritual

00:13:07.880 --> 00:13:10.910
giant in the spirit realm if you just

00:13:10.920 --> 00:13:14.189
put forth the effort to get there.

00:13:14.199 --> 00:13:16.269
God is no

00:13:16.269 --> 00:13:16.279
respecter

00:13:16.279 --> 00:13:17.910
of

00:13:17.920 --> 00:13:22.150
persons. What He did for

00:13:22.150 --> 00:13:22.160
Oral

00:13:22.160 --> 00:13:24.230
Roberts, for Katherine

00:13:24.230 --> 00:13:24.240
Kuhlman,

00:13:24.240 --> 00:13:28.069
for Billy Joe Daugherty, for Paul

00:13:28.069 --> 00:13:28.079
Daugherty

00:13:28.079 --> 00:13:29.750
across the

00:13:29.750 --> 00:13:29.760
street—what

00:13:29.760 --> 00:13:32.189
He did for them, He'll do for

00:13:32.199 --> 00:13:37.069
you. How big is your

00:13:37.069 --> 00:13:37.079
'want-to'for

00:13:37.079 --> 00:13:40.150
change in your life? Do you want it bad

00:13:40.160 --> 00:13:42.990
enough to do what they did to get

00:13:43.000 --> 00:13:46.110
it? They sacrificed. They

00:13:51.040 --> 00:13:54.430
believed

00:13:54.440 --> 00:13:56.870
in the spiritual laws that whatsoever a

00:13:56.880 --> 00:14:01.230
man sows, that will he also reap.

00:14:01.240 --> 00:14:03.189
I come here because I'm

00:14:03.199 --> 00:14:06.150
inspired that this is somebody's

00:14:06.160 --> 00:14:08.749
faith in

00:14:08.759 --> 00:14:11.389
action. Faith without works is dead, the

00:14:11.399 --> 00:14:14.230
Bible says. This is faith

00:14:14.240 --> 00:14:16.829
manifested.

00:14:21.519 --> 00:14:24.110
I see these buildings—started as a

00:14:24.120 --> 00:14:26.030
seed, started as a

00:14:26.040 --> 00:14:29.790
field. He

00:14:29.790 --> 00:14:29.800
was

00:14:29.800 --> 00:14:31.550
believing God for

00:14:31.560 --> 00:14:34.069
just this land and

00:14:35.399 --> 00:14:38.749
the farmer wouldn't sell it to him,

00:14:38.759 --> 00:14:40.949
but look: the

00:14:40.959 --> 00:14:44.509
vision from here produced all these buildings.

00:14:44.509 --> 00:14:44.519
It

00:14:44.519 --> 00:14:46.629
produced the church across the street. Paul Daugherty

00:14:46.629 --> 00:14:46.639
and them

00:14:46.639 --> 00:14:48.470
just latched onto

00:14:48.480 --> 00:14:50.629
the vision

00:14:50.639 --> 00:14:52.749
of this man.

00:14:52.759 --> 00:14:55.509
If you

00:14:55.519 --> 00:14:57.949
ever want to read about his testimony

00:14:57.959 --> 00:15:01.389
about all of ORU, it's in *The Ultimate

00:15:01.399 --> 00:15:03.790
Voice* by Oral Roberts. Oh, phenomenal book.

00:15:03.800 --> 00:15:06.990
Speaking about hearing God's voice, he

00:15:07.000 --> 00:15:09.550
talks about his testimony of ORU and how

00:15:09.560 --> 00:15:12.350
the miracle started.

00:15:17.990 --> 00:15:18.000
It's

00:15:22.720 --> 00:15:25.949
really a great book to

00:15:32.870 --> 00:15:32.880
read—life-changing.

00:15:37.399 --> 00:15:41.389
I was praying for

00:15:41.399 --> 00:15:43.550
ministers and the Lord spoke to me.

00:15:43.560 --> 00:15:44.870
I was praying for my son

00:15:44.880 --> 00:15:47.590
and always praying for

00:15:47.600 --> 00:15:50.590
your kids'future and for

00:15:50.600 --> 00:15:51.949
a godly

00:15:51.959 --> 00:15:55.590
spouse.

00:15:55.600 --> 00:15:59.030
Intercede for your children to

00:15:59.040 --> 00:16:02.110
find the right mate.

00:16:02.120 --> 00:16:04.389
I was driving around

00:16:04.399 --> 00:16:05.949
recently and the Lord

00:16:05.959 --> 00:16:08.350
spoke to me. He said, 'Brandon, many of

00:16:08.360 --> 00:16:11.949
My ministers have married a

00:16:11.959 --> 00:16:14.550
Delilah. I warned them and

00:16:14.550 --> 00:16:14.560
warned

00:16:14.560 --> 00:16:16.790
them not to marry

00:16:16.790 --> 00:16:16.800
certain

00:16:16.800 --> 00:16:19.030
individuals, and they marry them either

00:16:19.040 --> 00:16:21.829
out of lust of the eye, lust of the flesh,

00:16:21.839 --> 00:16:22.870
or

00:16:22.880 --> 00:16:26.110
whatever, and they're snared by a Delilah,

00:16:26.120 --> 00:16:29.269
just like Samson

00:16:29.269 --> 00:16:29.279
was.'I

00:16:29.279 --> 00:16:30.910
saw

00:16:30.920 --> 00:16:33.990
ministers trying to take off like a

00:16:34.000 --> 00:16:36.309
rocket because they had all this potential

00:16:36.319 --> 00:16:39.710
inside of them,

00:16:39.720 --> 00:16:43.069
but they had a rock—the Delilah—attached

00:16:43.069 --> 00:16:43.079
to the neck of the

00:16:43.079 --> 00:16:47.350
rocket.

00:16:47.360 --> 00:16:50.350
In

00:16:50.360 --> 00:16:53.110
the vision, I saw the

00:16:53.120 --> 00:16:55.269
rocket trying to take off, but it was

00:16:55.279 --> 00:16:58.590
only allowed to go so far

00:16:58.600 --> 00:17:00.189
because they were attached to a

00:17:00.199 --> 00:17:02.269
major rock called

00:17:02.269 --> 00:17:02.279
a

00:17:02.279 --> 00:17:05.710
Delilah. If you marry a

00:17:05.710 --> 00:17:05.720
Delilah—and

00:17:05.720 --> 00:17:08.069
the Bible says do not be unequally

00:17:08.069 --> 00:17:08.079
yoked

00:17:08.079 --> 00:17:10.829
with

00:17:10.829 --> 00:17:10.839
unbelievers—you

00:17:10.839 --> 00:17:14.429
have to

00:17:22.679 --> 00:17:25.829
link yourself up with somebody

00:17:25.839 --> 00:17:29.750
who is there to help you; iron

00:17:29.750 --> 00:17:29.760
sharpens

00:17:29.760 --> 00:17:31.830
iron.

00:17:46.760 --> 00:17:49.909
This was my warning to

00:17:49.919 --> 00:17:54.590
you young people: do not marry a

00:17:54.600 --> 00:17:58.270
Delilah. Do not marry an Ishmael; look for

00:17:58.280 --> 00:17:59.750
your Isaac.

00:17:59.760 --> 00:18:02.310
The devil will try to bring an Ishmael

00:18:02.310 --> 00:18:02.320
to you

00:18:02.320 --> 00:18:06.190
to try

00:18:06.200 --> 00:18:08.590
to get your ministry to not make it.

00:18:10.120 --> 00:18:13.110
You'll always be struggling,

00:18:18.120 --> 00:18:20.630
married to

00:18:20.640 --> 00:18:23.789
a Delilah. Now, if you married your

00:18:23.789 --> 00:18:23.799
Delilah,

00:18:23.799 --> 00:18:26.350
I believe there's still hope and that

00:18:26.360 --> 00:18:28.390
God will turn around what the enemy

00:18:29.600 --> 00:18:32.789
meant for bad.

00:18:32.799 --> 00:18:35.110
Some people just

00:18:35.120 --> 00:18:37.149
don't have it and they don't want

00:18:37.159 --> 00:18:39.590
it. They

00:18:41.280 --> 00:18:43.630
like

00:18:43.640 --> 00:18:46.350
the fame, they like the

00:18:46.360 --> 00:18:48.789
celebrity, they

00:18:48.799 --> 00:18:50.909
like the finances, but they're not there

00:18:50.919 --> 00:18:52.710
for the right

00:18:52.720 --> 00:18:57.110
reasons. So I warn you: don't marry a

00:18:57.120 --> 00:18:59.830
Delilah. The Lord has

00:18:59.840 --> 00:19:02.110
spoken to me and He said, 'Many of My

00:19:02.120 --> 00:19:04.430
ministers, Brandon, were called to go even

00:19:04.440 --> 00:19:06.430
higher than what they are, but they

00:19:06.440 --> 00:19:09.149
married the wrong

00:19:14.520 --> 00:19:16.710
people.'Now,

00:19:22.240 --> 00:19:24.149
you say, 'Should I divorce

00:19:24.149 --> 00:19:24.159
them?'Heavens

00:19:24.159 --> 00:19:25.950
no. I'm not trying to advocate

00:19:25.960 --> 00:19:28.630
that. You pray for them. You

00:19:32.280 --> 00:19:34.870
made a

00:19:34.880 --> 00:19:39.149
choice, you made a covenant,

00:19:45.960 --> 00:19:50.029
so now you have integrity and you

00:19:50.039 --> 00:19:52.470
intercede. It

00:19:52.480 --> 00:19:53.909
just could have been

00:19:53.919 --> 00:19:56.510
an

00:19:56.520 --> 00:19:59.710
easier path.

00:19:59.720 --> 00:20:02.590
I'm

00:20:02.600 --> 00:20:04.390
trying to tell you, if you're single and

00:20:04.400 --> 00:20:05.909
the Lord is

00:20:05.919 --> 00:20:07.029
warning you

00:20:07.039 --> 00:20:11.350
today: listen to the voice

00:20:11.360 --> 00:20:14.750
of the Lord. Life has obstacles,

00:20:14.750 --> 00:20:14.760
and

00:20:14.760 --> 00:20:17.950
it matters

00:20:17.960 --> 00:20:20.110
who you link yourself up with. You

00:20:20.110 --> 00:20:20.120
don't want

00:20:20.120 --> 00:20:21.590
to be

00:20:21.590 --> 00:20:21.600
dragging

00:20:24.830 --> 00:20:24.840
a

00:20:26.230 --> 00:20:26.240
Delilah

00:20:26.240 --> 00:20:28.470
behind

00:20:28.480 --> 00:20:29.669
you

00:20:29.679 --> 00:20:31.350
while

00:20:31.360 --> 00:20:33.149
God says, 'Get up to the

00:20:39.710 --> 00:20:39.720
summit.'Be

00:20:47.000 --> 00:20:50.110
very vigilant about this

00:20:50.120 --> 00:20:51.750
because this is a tactic of the

00:20:51.760 --> 00:20:53.590
enemy.

00:20:58.400 --> 00:21:00.669
The devil will send an Ishmael; the

00:21:00.679 --> 00:21:02.470
devil will send a Delilah. You have

00:21:02.480 --> 00:21:05.710
to say, 'Who's in your life that's cutting

00:21:05.720 --> 00:21:08.870
your hair

00:21:08.880 --> 00:21:11.590
and trying to gouge

00:21:11.600 --> 00:21:15.310
out your

00:21:15.310 --> 00:21:15.320
eyes?'stealing

00:21:15.320 --> 00:21:16.789
the vision of what God's called you

00:21:16.799 --> 00:21:20.029
to do.

00:21:41.360 --> 00:21:45.669
Find your Esther today;

00:21:45.679 --> 00:21:47.830
don't line up with your

00:21:47.830 --> 00:21:47.840
Delilah.

00:21:47.840 --> 00:21:50.350
I feel the power of the Lord on

00:21:50.360 --> 00:21:53.269
that today.

00:21:56.279 --> 00:21:58.590
There's some of you out there that God's

00:21:58.600 --> 00:22:01.110
trying to shake.

00:22:01.120 --> 00:22:05.710
It's time to believe God for

00:22:05.720 --> 00:22:09.470
big. Don't

00:22:09.480 --> 00:22:13.830
lose

00:22:13.830 --> 00:22:13.840
faith.

00:22:13.840 --> 00:22:15.789
You say, 'Well, I've messed

00:22:15.799 --> 00:22:17.430
up my life. I've

00:22:21.279 --> 00:22:23.350
derailed

00:22:23.360 --> 00:22:26.029
my life so much that God can't use

00:22:26.029 --> 00:22:26.039
me.'But

00:22:26.039 --> 00:22:29.269
the Lord told me to tell you:

00:22:29.279 --> 00:22:31.350
what the devil meant for bad and

00:22:31.360 --> 00:22:33.230
the traps you've been

00:22:33.230 --> 00:22:33.240
snared in—the

00:22:33.240 --> 00:22:34.990
very pit you've fallen into—God's going

00:22:35.000 --> 00:22:37.590
to deliver you out of them all if you

00:22:37.600 --> 00:22:41.190
just seek Him and repent.

00:22:44.039 --> 00:22:46.430
The best is yet to come. If you're

00:22:46.440 --> 00:22:48.710
single and you are believing God for a

00:22:48.720 --> 00:22:52.310
spouse, I would definitely recommend you

00:22:52.320 --> 00:22:55.230
to write a list—write your

00:22:55.240 --> 00:22:57.789
vision and make it plain. That's

00:22:57.799 --> 00:22:59.750
what Diana and I both did when we didn't even

00:22:59.760 --> 00:23:02.110
know each other. I

00:23:02.120 --> 00:23:05.149
made a very

00:23:05.159 --> 00:23:07.110
specific, detailed list of everything I

00:23:07.120 --> 00:23:08.710
was believing God for

00:23:08.710 --> 00:23:08.720
in

00:23:08.720 --> 00:23:11.230
a mate. He

00:23:11.240 --> 00:23:12.789
did the same thing.

00:23:19.000 --> 00:23:22.750
When we met,

00:23:24.799 --> 00:23:27.990
we got out our lists

00:23:27.990 --> 00:23:28.000
and

00:23:28.000 --> 00:23:30.190
read them to each other, and it

00:23:30.200 --> 00:23:31.149
was exactly—to

00:23:31.149 --> 00:23:31.159
a T—like

00:23:31.159 --> 00:23:33.870
I had

00:23:33.880 --> 00:23:35.909
written it about Brandon and he had

00:23:35.919 --> 00:23:39.430
written it about me. I believe

00:23:39.440 --> 00:23:41.669
it works.

00:23:49.200 --> 00:23:52.669
I believe that God will give

00:23:52.679 --> 00:23:55.269
you the desires of your

00:23:55.279 --> 00:23:58.510
heart.

00:24:22.840 --> 00:24:25.590
You can pray for

00:24:25.600 --> 00:24:28.630
your future spouse right now,

00:24:28.640 --> 00:24:30.870
that the Lord keeps them

00:24:30.870 --> 00:24:30.880
protected

00:24:30.880 --> 00:24:32.870
and

00:24:32.880 --> 00:24:35.750
set apart,

00:24:37.480 --> 00:24:40.510
that they're not being snared by

00:24:40.520 --> 00:24:42.950
wickedness and

00:24:42.960 --> 00:24:44.710
the lust and desires of the

00:24:44.720 --> 00:24:47.389
flesh, that they remain on

00:24:47.399 --> 00:24:49.269
fire for God.

00:24:51.120 --> 00:24:54.230
Any

00:24:54.240 --> 00:24:55.870
snares that the devil sends their way,

00:24:55.880 --> 00:24:57.710
they overcome

00:24:57.720 --> 00:24:59.350
them by the blood of the Lamb and by the word

00:24:59.360 --> 00:25:02.789
of their testimony.

00:25:02.789 --> 00:25:02.799
You've

00:25:02.799 --> 00:25:04.510
got to continue to do it.

00:25:07.159 --> 00:25:08.590
You

00:25:08.600 --> 00:25:10.630
don't just visit the anointing;

00:25:12.799 --> 00:25:15.950
you live there. Diana and I choose to live there.

00:25:29.000 --> 00:25:31.750
It's not convenient to drive

00:25:31.760 --> 00:25:34.149
so far over here to ORU—I live a long

00:25:34.149 --> 00:25:34.159
way

00:25:34.159 --> 00:25:38.070
from here—but I choose to do it

00:25:38.080 --> 00:25:40.389
to make this a habit.

00:25:40.399 --> 00:25:42.350
My son said when we went to Florida,

00:25:42.360 --> 00:25:45.190
'Man, I missed going to ORU, Dad, because there's a presence there.'It blesses me because I believe in raising godly children and keeping them set apart for their spouse. Megan's back there; she hears. We're believing God for Megan. I hope this video inspired you to believe God to 'make no little plans here.'I love the little prayer tower over there. Diana and I are going to pray for you. I want you to believe God for bigger. Donald Trump has his meeting on Friday. Somebody called and said, 'Hey Brandon, did you know that there's a big crypto meeting on Friday?'Folks, we're at the point of liftoff. Something major is about to take place for the body of Christ. God is about to bring forth all the seeds that you've sowed in the past. You've got to take the seed that you have and plant it so that God has something to work with. If you do nothing, you're going to get nothing. Sew your time at your church! Volunteer, clean bathrooms, and believe God for a job. There's something you can do to sew your time at your local church. I remember when we had no seed to give, we had one hundred dollars that we needed for our electric bill. The Lord told Diana, 'Take that hundred dollars and go to the thrift store, and I'm going to teach you how to multiply that.'Once we started tithing, the miracles started happening. We always tithe first because you give to God first. I'll be real: we were once forced to tithe at our jobs at a church, and if you did not tithe, they fired you. My attitude was not happy about that at first, but it trained us. I told the Lord, 'You either take care of us or I quit.'And He told me, 'Brandon, I've called you to be here. I need you to pray for that man.'And He told me he was going to lose his church, and he did. But I stuck by what the Lord told me to do for thirteen years. We sacrificed making nothing, and then He started teaching me how to do things. When Diana came up with the idea of doing eBay and Poshmark, that's when our life started to change drastically. I could not see how used t-shirts at a thrift store could pay a bill, but come to find out, people wanted those shirts. They like those band tees. If the Lord tells you that shirt right there is a vintage t-shirt, sell it! It might look stinky with holes in it, but somebody wanted it. Whenever we started tithing, the

00:25:45.190 --> 00:25:45.200
miracles started happening. There was that one time when the children didn't have shoes, but that day I looked down and there was a twenty-dollar bill laying on the ground in my direct path. Praise God! That's how my God works. I walked in and they had a sale on the shoes, and that twenty dollars got the shoes the kids needed. Never forget the miracles from the past. We created a book of miracles just to smear it in the devil's face every day. Have a 'stacking rocks'experience to go back to and say, 'This is where God came through.'If He did it once, He will do it again. The devil's not afraid of you having one miracle; what he's afraid of is you having multiple miracles—volumes of them. I remember the time Tim came up and said, 'Brandon, I don't know

00:25:45.200 --> 00:25:52.669
why, but my wife, Janet, said the Lord told us to give you a thousand dollars.'I almost passed out. It was a shock and awe moment on December 22nd. We were not going to go out and ask, because we're not in the ministry of 'dropping hints,'but He came through. That's one of my stacking rocks moments. We're just real; we have issues, folks, but we choose to focus on Jesus. Our marriage gets stronger because of it. We pray together, we fast together, we take communion together as a family. We spend hours in the car

00:25:52.669 --> 00:25:52.679
